        "description": "Returns a page of records, defaulting to 10 per page. Change 'page' to  \nnavigate (page=1, page=2, ...) and 'size' to control how many records are  \nreturned per page. Service method is annotated with @Transactional(readOnly = true)."
      },
      "response": []
